  "prompt": "What are the signs that a Taurus man really likes you?",
  "response": "When a Taurus man is genuinely interested in you, he will show his feelings through consistent, thoughtful, and affectionate actions. Here are some signs that a Taurus man really likes you:\n\n### 1. **He\u2019s Consistent and Reliable**\n   - Taurus men value stability, so if he likes you, he\u2019ll make an effort to be dependable and present in your life. He\u2019ll keep his promises and follow through on plans.\n\n### 2. **He Wants to Spend Quality Time With You**\n   - He\u2019ll prioritize spending time with you, whether it\u2019s cozy nights in, romantic dinners, or shared activities he knows you enjoy.\n\n### 3. **He\u2019s Generous**\n   - Taurus men are known for their generosity. If he likes you, he\u2019ll go out of his way to give you thoughtful gifts, cook for you, or take care of your needs.\n\n### 4. **He\u2019s Affectionate and Physical**\n   - Taurus is a sensual sign, so he\u2019ll show his interest through physical touch, like holding your hand, hugging, or cuddling.\n\n### 5. **He Opens Up to You**\n   - Taurus men can be reserved, but if he trusts you, he\u2019ll share his thoughts, feelings, and personal stories with you.\n\n### 6. **He Introduces You to His Inner Circle**\n   - If he likes you, he\u2019ll want you to meet his close friends and family, as he values long-term connections.\n\n### 7. **He Remembers Details About You**\n   - A Taurus man pays attention to the little things. If he remembers your favorite foods, hobbies, or important dates, it\u2019s a sign he\u2019s invested in you.\n\n### 8. **He Talks About the Future**\n   - Taurus men are goal-oriented and practical. If he includes you in his future plans or talks about building a life together, it\u2019s a strong indicator of his feelings.\n\n### 9. **He\u2019s Protective**\n   - He\u2019ll naturally want to take care of you and make sure you\u2019re safe and comfortable.\n\n### 10. **He\u2019s Patient and Understanding**\n   - Taurus men are known for their patience. If he\u2019s willing to take things slow and understands your needs, it\u2019s a sign he\u2019s serious about you.\n\n### 11. **He Compliments You**\n   - Taurus men appreciate beauty and will often compliment your appearance, personality, or talents when they\u2019re attracted to you.\n\n### 12. **He Goes Out of His Way for You**\n   - If he\u2019s genuinely interested, he\u2019ll make an effort to support you, help you, or surprise you with gestures that show he cares.\n\nIf you notice these behaviors consistently, it\u2019s a strong sign that a Taurus man has real feelings for you. Remember, Taurus men take their time to build trust and commit, so patience is key!",
